data.description: This charming 4 bed, 2 bath home sits on .24 acres and is ready for you to move into and start making memories! Upgrades include fresh paint and new lvp flooring! Both bathrooms have been completely renovated! While you'll find a laundry room in the basement, additional laundry hookups are included on the main level in the kitchen. The garage and mud room provide extra storage space and can even be used as a craft/work area. Additional off street parking along the side of the attached garage - Rv storage/parking. This home is conveniently located close to two city parks and a community pool, perfect for family outings. Make this home yours and come see it today!
